# Core Features

## Dough Calculator

### Inputs

* Number of pizzas
* Dough ball weight
* Flour amount
* Water amount
* Hydration %
* Salt %
* Yeast %
* Selected pizzaiolo

### Outputs

* Flour
* Water
* Salt
* Yeast
* Total dough weight

### Formula

```text
Flour = TotalDough / (1 + Hydration + Salt + Yeast)

Water = Flour × Hydration

Salt = Flour × Salt%

Yeast = Flour × Yeast%
```

All calculations must update in real time.

