# Fermentation Planner

Inputs:

* Room temperature
* Fridge temperature
* Desired bake time

Outputs:

* Bulk fermentation duration
* Cold fermentation duration
* Balling time
* Fridge entry time
* Fridge exit time
* Estimated readiness

Timeline visualization required.

---

# Poolish Calculator

Inputs:

* Total flour
* Poolish percentage

Outputs:

* Poolish flour
* Poolish water
* Poolish yeast

Typical default:

```text
Poolish Flour = 50%

Poolish Water = 100% of Poolish Flour

Poolish Yeast = 0.1%
```

---

# Biga Calculator

Inputs:

* Total flour
* Biga percentage

Outputs:

* Biga flour
* Biga water
* Biga yeast

Default hydration:

```text
45%
```

---

# Sauce Calculator

Default:

