---

# Dough Temperature Calculator

Inputs:

* Room temperature
* Flour temperature
* Friction factor

Target:

```text
23°C
```

Formula:

```text
Water Temperature =
(3 × Target Dough Temp)
− Room Temp
− Flour Temp
− Friction Factor
```

---

# Yeast Converter

Convert between:

* Instant Dry Yeast
* Fresh Yeast
* Active Dry Yeast

Approximate conversions:

```text
Fresh = Instant × 3

Active Dry = Instant × 1.25
```

